blockquote>17分 會唔會試下放 EdU ECE HD 先<br />\n讀2年就有牌 之後可以讀番PT Degree <br />\n而且今年好似有400個HD位</blockquote><br />\n多謝你回覆先。但點解唔直接讀Degree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢已經有學士offer</blockquote><br />\nEdU 認受性應該係最高<br />\n其實HD收生個平均分係18  17分去報已經係搏下<br />\n另外HD有政府資助會慳好多<br />\n學費平過BU好多"},{"pid":"31d1ab47fecee0a7fa527deadd786100c2c4fa59","tid":318980,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"Agger 樓上<br />\nEdu 既HD係幼教呢行認受好高 <br />\n而且好過BU degree"},{"pid":"8e4aa52b697a78dd46be1d7e2ff462808e8c90c2","tid":318980,"uid":15753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"EdU HD點都好過BU自資<br />\n其實幼教冇咁著重de唔degree<br />\n學校口卑緊要啲<br />\n反正HD兩年後有牌 好多人都係做住野再補part time degree<br />\n<br />\n記得放band a <br />\n因為一定要in先收 但只in放band a嘅人"},{"pid":"bb6705be61288331072f4288e9ac09f760a66e28","tid":318980,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"聽過 講口碑 ive 仲好過BU <br />\n其實幼教hd同degree分別係<br />\n一個係有牌做老師 一個係有資格做主任管理級<br />\n不過幼稚園根本好難或做好多年先升到去主任/校長<br />\n所以好多人選擇遲下再讀PT Degree <br />\n<br />\n前題係 真係好有心做幼師<br />\nHD 好chur  yr1  sem 2已經要係咁實習"},{"pid":"69117313e23c8422c6673a8f3c00428e132a01e3","tid":318980,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得120個位好多人入唔到，除左教大最好既幼教degree</blockquote><br />\n120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2016/2017個年係，今年唔知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咩120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大既幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。聽你咁講，都係讀BU 幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無記錯教大HD係300幾400個 degree 係20個"},{"pid":"e8a47048d81fef3410daf562989b1eba691f0198","tid":318980,"uid":89096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得120個位好多人入唔到，除左教大最好既幼教degree</blockquote><br />\n120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2016/2017個年係，今年唔知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咩120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大既幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。聽你咁講，都係讀BU 幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無記錯教大HD係300幾400個 degree 係20個</blockquote><br />\n120個位係bu幼教degree呀，我上年有報但唔收，得33233"},{"pid":"367caab490ddc52978e69f7bf663bf7f401f5efb","tid":318980,"uid":63211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得120個位好多人入唔到，除左教大最好既幼教degree</blockquote><br />\n120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2016/2017個年係，今年唔知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咩120個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大既幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。聽你咁講，都係讀BU 幼教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無記錯教大HD係300幾400個 degree 係20個</blockquote><br />\n咁少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6d4f824922562fb5dbc5bc03ecc1dc56ff1c2a","tid":318980,"uid":80138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"其實佢真係有心讀 <br />\n屋企又應付到開支<br />\n我會覺得讀BU degree <br />\n因為遲早都係要讀 <br />\n在職讀返個degree好辛苦<br />\n而且bu認受性唔係好低 出面都好多老師係bu出黎做野 <br />\n不過叫你呀妹再諗清楚啦"},{"pid":"2a9c5c